# Reown AppKit Integration Guide

## Overview
This project uses Reown AppKit (formerly WalletConnect) for wallet connection and management.

## Installation
```bash
npm install @reown/appkit @reown/appkit-adapter-wagmi
```

## Configuration

### 1. Get Project ID
- Visit https://cloud.reown.com
- Create a new project
- Copy your Project ID

### 2. Environment Variables
```env
NEXT_PUBLIC_REOWN_PROJECT_ID=your_project_id_here
```

### 3. Setup (Already Done)
- `src/config/wagmi.ts` - Wagmi adapter configuration
- `src/components/WagmiProviderWrapper.tsx` - AppKit initialization

## Usage

### Connect Button
```tsx
// Use the built-in AppKit button
<appkit-button size="lg" />
```

### Check Connection Status
```tsx
import { useAccount } from 'wagmi';

const { address, isConnected } = useAccount();
```

### Access Wallet
```tsx
import { useAppKitAccount } from '@reown/appkit/react';

const { address, isConnected } = useAppKitAccount();
```

